{"tid":2455851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"數百艘中國武裝漁船入侵菲律賓海域","createTime":"2021-03-21T12:34:44.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T17:17:17.000Z","uid":125168,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"fca9bf123adf3d356274038e47807044c0f48754","tid":2455851,"uid":125168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:34:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581718-20210321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581718-20210321.htm&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfW0Q%2Fwx8zutUsTDhO6XOofs%3D&h=2cbc1266\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1581718-20210321.htm&h=8dea39c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1581718-20210321.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓政府對在有主權爭議的南海，發現數百艘中國船隻表達關切。<br />\n<br />\n《路透社》報道，菲律賓海岸防衛隊通報，本月7日在屬於菲律賓的專屬經濟區內的牛軛礁，發現220艘中國漁船集結，相信是由中國海上民兵駕駛，船隻一字排開。<br />\n<br />\n菲律賓當局指，漁船當時並非捕漁，但他們關注過度捕撈、破壞海洋環境、以及航行安全的風險。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部並未作出回應。"},{"pid":"6ee8b7221e0abf055d4165ad6e618d0ee5fa8f79","tid":2455851,"uid":7043,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"武裝漁船呢個terms 真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e44876a97079cb80ca2035a3de8104716da77f","tid":2455851,"uid":74009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:45:51.000Z","msg":"我黨做乜都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都冇人屌得郁"},{"pid":"a8aaa5d698e80d1e48bcbb42d6ffcf92203f4484","tid":2455851,"uid":387466,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"6ee8b7221e0abf055d4165ad6e618d0ee5fa8f79","tid":2455851,"uid":7043,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:44:45.000Z","msg":"武裝漁船呢個terms 真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T12:46:47.